Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo parece estar bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Fiquei com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Logo aparecerá uma ilha à nossa frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Permitam-me fazer uma introdução.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:03.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ao redor de Whole Cake Island, \Nhá trinta e quatro ilhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Tantas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Cada uma delas é governada por um ministro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse território marítimo é conhecido como...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...Totto Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:26.95,Title,,0,0,420,,Totto Land{\fad(1500,1000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Pensei que fosse um navio inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu roubei de alguns piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou levá-lo pessoalmente para mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem algo doce no navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, mama ficará feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma surpresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Não informem mama sobre o navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, que maravilhoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pekoms-sama, você é tão inteligente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Tanto os tijolos quanto as casas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...é feito de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma cidade de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece um sonho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:02.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Há todo tipo de gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos está acontecendo nesta cidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Está saindo chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, vou começar pela fonte de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A chocofonte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.53,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2370,2870)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.53,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2370,2870)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.53,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2370,2870)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.53,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2370,2870)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.53,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2370,2870)}Banho de chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Banho de chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.53,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Banho de chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Um banho de chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Roupas de chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Você pode comê-las?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Consegui enganá-los, mas\N não por muito tempo-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos apressar e fazer o que precisamos fazer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Terminaram?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Que fofo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nami, você está maravilhosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, olhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu vestido também não está mal, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, está maravilhoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,E aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pareço uma pirata, Broo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Quer mais?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji está agora em Whole Cake Island e levará mais um dia para chegarmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão comprar comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Pedro, você tem binóculos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muitas raças aqui, Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Também há mink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,É um lugar maravilhoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, esse é o sonho de mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:06:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Humanos, mink, homens-peixe, \Nbraços-longos, pernas-longas, anões...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Um país onde todas as raças\N possam viver sem discriminação.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, onde todos possam viver assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, esse é o ideal de mama, Totto Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Considerem um país enorme.{\an8}{\fad(0,646)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Esta é a Ilha Cacau, governada \Npelo Ministro do Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,A cidade se chama Chocola Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Chocola Town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Que nome legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo na cidade é feito de chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu adoro chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Posso comer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nesta cidade, você pode\N comer até explodir-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas tenha cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,É ilegal comer o \Nchocolate das telhas das casas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque não poderão se proteger\N da chuva nem da neve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,O vidro das janelas pertence à jurisdição do Ministro dos Doces e as colunas ao Ministro dos Biscoitos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:07:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo o que não for chocolate, \Né propriedade privada ou propriedade pública!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece delicioso...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Não entendi direito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, as calcinhas também são de chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Que vontade de ver chococalcinhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, não viemos para descansar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Voltem assim que terminarem de comprar-gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou ficar no navio porque me conhecem, mas eu adoro chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Me tragam um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você for, não perca tempo e se disfarce...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy e Chopper já estão na cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que vocês acham que vai acontecer comigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...se descobrirem que eu os trouxe aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ajam com cautela!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Logo saberemos onde eles estão.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles comeram uma cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Não brinquem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Se fossem apenas as paredes de chocolate, poderíamos consertar depois,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.80,Main,,0,0,0,,mas a cafeteria inteira desapareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles mexeram com doces, \Nmarshmallows, amêndoas e gomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Cometeram o crime de dano\N à propriedade por comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou investigar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Acompanhem-me à delegacia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas, velho, eu tenho uma boa razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Estava delicioso demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.74,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Estava delicioso demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, já cansei de vocês, idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou prender vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles vão ser capturados!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Não lute, Pedro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, senhor chocopolicial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Tapete, tapete...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,O tapete está voando...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Tapete, tapete...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, a dona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, mais problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,A dona da cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Observe o estado do seu negócio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso acreditar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.22,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(496,0)}A DONA DO CAFÉ "CARAMELO"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.18,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(390,0)}NITRO, A GELATINA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.93,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(390,0)}RABIYAN, O TAPETE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês deixaram tanto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso não foi o que combinamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Se responsabilizem por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, você conhece ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,E o que é aquilo no ombro dela?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Pensei que a combinação de geleia, biscoitos e chocolate era deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Peguem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Comam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Gostaram?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Está delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.64,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Está delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, senhor chocopolicial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,O café ia vencer logo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,então pedi que comessem tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sabia que eram desmanteladores!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Devem colocar uma placa enquanto trabalham.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda havia alguns clientes dentro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, vou indo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpem por todo esse alvoroço!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Uau, não foi nada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, era um alarme falso.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, é verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Parabéns pelo seu casamento, Pudding-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Será em breve e ainda assim você cuida do negócio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não trabalhe demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos queremos que você seja feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Salvou Luffy e Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela é gentil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem será?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Que sorte eles têm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar do próximo Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Capitão Pedro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,É o nosso Capitão Pedro, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Vim passear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não conte a ninguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma honra vê-lo novamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Você conhece alguém nesta cidade, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Conto depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Então você se chama Pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por nos ajudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:04.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu é que deveria agradecer a vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,É que vocês disseram...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Estava delicioso demais".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,O chocolate daquela cafeteria \Nfoi feito por mim com uma nova receita!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Como derreteu na boca de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Adicionei leite à manteiga de cacau e ao açúcar puro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...e amassei por três dias a 29 graus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Não entendi, mas estava delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Fazem-me chorar quando dizem que estava delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico muito feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Q-Que garota tão boa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Você gosta de fazer chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu adoro coisas doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Toda a cidade cheira a chocolate, é um paraíso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Até a mesa é feita de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Gostaríamos de agradecer como merece, Pudding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas temos algo a fazer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:04.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, que tal tomarem uma xícara de chá?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ficou um gosto doce na boca, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Seria ótimo tomar chá!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Esperem um momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, que garota boa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela é realmente uma boa garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não perguntei seus nomes, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.65,Main,,0,0,0,,O homem que será o Rei dos...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
